          "preview": "# Architecture\n\n## Overview\nlaunchpad-studio is a tiny Node ESM release-planning toolkit that normalizes feature requests into release cards.\n\n## Core Modules\n\n### src/index.js\nEntry point. Re-exports planner, format, and validate helpers.\n\n### src/planner.js\nExports `normalizeFeature(request)` → `{id, title, description, type, effort, priority}`.\n\n### src/format.js\nExports `card(feature)` → pretty-printed release card string.\n\n### src/validate.js\nExports `isValidFeature(obj)` → boolean schema check.\n\n## Testing\nUses built-in `node:test` and `node:assert`. All modules covered."
