          "type": "file",
          "size": 567,
          "preview": "# Usage\n\n## CLI\n\n```bash\nnpx launchpad-studio <feature-request.json\n```\n\n## Programmatic\n\n```js\nimport { planRelease } from 'launchpad-studio';\n\nconst cards = planRelease({\n  title: 'Dark-mode support',\n  description: 'Users want a toggle for dark mode',\n  scope: ['ui', 'theme']\n});\n```\n\n## Output\n\nReturns an array of release cards:\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": \"feat-dark-mode\",\n    \"title\": \"Dark-mode support\",\n    \"description\": \"Users want a toggle for dark mode\",\n    \"type\": \"feature\",\n    \"scope\": [\"ui\", \"theme\"],\n    \"priority\": 1,\n    \"estimate\": 3\n  }\n]\n```"
